2^6=64\equiv9\pmod{55}
\displaystyle\implies 18^{17}=2^{17}\cdot 9^{17}\equiv 2^{17}\cdot(2^6)^{17}\pmod{55}\equiv2^{17+6\cdot17}=2^{119}
\displaystyle\implies 2^{119}\equiv 2^{-1} \pmod{55}
